WEBVTT

00:01.314 --> 00:04.124
I love that you were
named after Bob Dylan.

00:08.488 --> 00:09.899
Bob Dylan.

00:09.989 --> 00:10.967
(ANIMALS CALLING)

00:14.961 --> 00:17.840
LILY: You hear that sound?
Those are lemurs.

00:17.931 --> 00:21.708
They're primates, they sound like
people laughing in the distance.

00:21.801 --> 00:23.246
DYLAN: They freak me out.

00:23.870 --> 00:25.577
You sound like a lemur.

00:26.039 --> 00:27.040
LILY: What?

00:27.140 --> 00:29.643
I'm worried Lily's gonna hurt Dylan.

00:29.776 --> 00:32.655
No, it's gonna be the other way around.

00:32.779 --> 00:35.157
Well, how do you figure that?

00:35.281 --> 00:38.421
'Cause she's a farm girl, Ben... jamin.

00:38.518 --> 00:40.657
And,

00:40.787 --> 00:44.599
he's like this exotic
creature from the city.

00:44.691 --> 00:48.104
- Exotic? My son?
- (LAUGHING) Yes.

00:50.129 --> 00:53.576
I was afraid you thought
he was a little bit of a jerk.

00:55.869 --> 00:58.907
I'm guessing that Rosie was more like
your wife and Dylan's more like you

00:59.005 --> 01:00.643
and that's why you're so hard on him.

01:04.777 --> 01:08.190
I want you to know,
I think you're incredibly pretty.

01:10.016 --> 01:12.428
Please, don't take offense
if I don't hit on you.

01:12.519 --> 01:13.998
I'd be offended if you did.

01:15.054 --> 01:16.032
Good.

01:16.155 --> 01:18.157
I'm a big fan of people
being exactly who they are.

01:18.291 --> 01:20.100
- Exactly.
- So we think alike.

01:20.193 --> 01:21.194
We do.

01:21.327 --> 01:23.466
And if I wanted to be kissed by you,
you wouldn't have a choice.

01:24.998 --> 01:27.103
Thank you. I think.

01:27.200 --> 01:28.941
I don't doubt that.

01:29.035 --> 01:31.208
- What did we just say?
- I don't know.

01:31.337 --> 01:32.873
Okay.

01:37.944 --> 01:39.116
(SIGHS)

01:41.748 --> 01:43.989
it's a lot to take on. All of us.

01:47.587 --> 01:49.191
I'll see you tomorrow, right?

