51:19.177 --> 51:21.919
It's all right. It doesn't hurt that bad.

51:22.213 --> 51:23.817
- Good job.
- Thank you.

51:23.948 --> 51:26.326
Thanks for saving the animals.

51:26.450 --> 51:29.021
- Thank you. Thanks.
- Good job.

51:32.490 --> 51:33.867
Home Depot.

51:35.826 --> 51:37.305
Well done.

