51:50.508 --> 51:53.148
I have 'em. Yeah, got 'em. Got 'em.

51:53.244 --> 51:54.655
Great.

51:55.880 --> 51:59.851
I got a big crush on you,
and I just can't get a handle on it, so.

52:08.726 --> 52:10.137
Congratulations.

52:11.729 --> 52:13.640
Congratulations to you.

52:16.000 --> 52:17.206
(MOANS)

52:27.111 --> 52:29.352
And if we're standing
near each other on New Year's,

52:29.447 --> 52:31.393
we'll do this again sometime.

52:33.584 --> 52:35.757
I look forward to New Year's.

52:43.928 --> 52:45.703
Look over here, guys.

52:46.697 --> 52:50.406
Just be yourself. This one's for Spar.

52:50.534 --> 52:51.604
Say, "Peaches."

52:51.736 --> 52:53.340
BOTH: Peaches.

52:53.437 --> 52:55.781
DYLAN: All right.
Give me that camera. Say, "Spar."

52:55.906 --> 52:57.078
BOTH: Spar.

52:57.208 --> 52:58.881
BENJAMIN: And one more of me
just throwing her over.

52:58.976 --> 53:00.751
- ROSIE: Dump me there inside the fence.
- Ready, one, two, three.

53:00.845 --> 53:02.688
Ready? One, two, three!

53:02.780 --> 53:03.758
(LAUGHING)

53:05.483 --> 53:08.930
If you had to choose between
people and animals, really quick,

53:09.053 --> 53:10.430
how would you choose?

53:10.554 --> 53:11.931
BENJAMIN: I want to get a shot of that.

53:12.056 --> 53:13.262
ROSIE: I'll get a close-up on your nose.

53:21.632 --> 53:23.043
Me, too.

53:23.601 --> 53:25.512
People!
(LAUGHS)

53:29.774 --> 53:32.482
- You goofball.
(LAUGHING)

54:29.066 --> 54:30.204
(SCREECHES)

54:40.077 --> 54:41.317
(GROWLS)

54:46.350 --> 54:48.557
- We bought a zoo.
- We did that.

54:48.652 --> 54:49.653
(CHUCKLES)

54:54.125 --> 54:56.435
DUNCAN: You only have to be courageous
for 20 seconds.

54:57.027 --> 54:59.940
BENJAMIN: <i>It has guided
me my entire life.</i>

55:00.064 --> 55:02.010
- All right. Ladies first.
- Where are we going?

55:05.302 --> 55:08.681
Now, hang on. So, okay. Stop.

55:08.773 --> 55:10.184
She was

55:11.041 --> 55:12.019
right there.

55:12.109 --> 55:16.683
This is the moment where both of you
became a possibility.

55:16.781 --> 55:18.852
I love that you're telling stories again.

55:18.949 --> 55:21.657
This is the story before the story.

55:21.752 --> 55:25.666
This is where you and you begin.

55:25.756 --> 55:28.828
Because this is where I met your mom.

55:29.293 --> 55:32.331
She was sitting right there in that chair.

55:36.200 --> 55:37.577
Hang on.

55:43.307 --> 55:44.786
Hey, hey. So,

55:44.909 --> 55:46.286
I was walkin' by.

55:48.879 --> 55:52.952
And I saw her and I literally stopped,
like this, just stopped.

55:53.083 --> 55:55.791
And went, "Oh, my God."

55:55.920 --> 55:59.925
"That is the most beautiful woman
I have ever seen in my entire life."

56:00.057 --> 56:01.434
But I've never done anything like this.

56:01.559 --> 56:04.369
I'd never gone and talked
to a total stranger before.

56:04.462 --> 56:06.703
But she was right there.

56:06.797 --> 56:11.075
And so I thought to myself,
"20 seconds." Right?

56:12.336 --> 56:13.747
Go.

56:18.509 --> 56:22.116
Now I'm in the restaurant.
And I'm terrified.

56:22.680 --> 56:24.091
Thinkin' about leaving.

56:24.181 --> 56:26.787
I can actually touch her.
She's right there.

56:26.917 --> 56:28.590
She still hasn't seen me.

56:28.686 --> 56:30.324
And I still have 15
seconds of courage left.

56:30.988 --> 56:32.399
I'm goin' for it.

56:33.757 --> 56:35.134
Bravery.

56:35.559 --> 56:37.561
Here's what I said.

56:45.002 --> 56:46.413
What?

56:47.638 --> 56:48.708
(SIGHS)

56:49.907 --> 56:51.580
I said,

56:52.743 --> 56:54.745
"Excuse me."

57:16.033 --> 57:17.444
Hi, Mom.

57:17.535 --> 57:19.014
Hi, Mommy.

57:27.044 --> 57:30.514
"Why would an amazing woman like you"

57:30.648 --> 57:33.993
"even talk to someone like me?"

57:40.658 --> 57:41.898
(CHUCKLES)

57:42.493 --> 57:43.904
Why not?

57:44.295 --> 57:46.571
(<i>GATHERING STORIES</i> PLAYING)

58:34.144 --> 58:36.886
<i>You made me long for.</i>

58:37.948 --> 58:40.292
<i>To be a part of.</i>

58:41.719 --> 58:44.962
<i>Something that I can't see.</i>

58:45.389 --> 58:47.926
<i>A life that is beyond.</i>

58:49.493 --> 58:52.702
<i>Something that I can't fear.</i>

58:53.364 --> 58:55.708
<i>To be a part of.</i>

58:57.101 --> 59:00.548
<i>The story, it belongs to you.</i>

59:16.353 --> 59:19.357
<i>Something you said burns.</i>

59:19.523 --> 59:22.470
<i>Apart the pen and the paper.</i>

59:24.094 --> 59:26.438
<i>You can't always write it.</i>

59:27.297 --> 59:31.040
<i>It is something you have to do.</i>

59:31.735 --> 59:34.011
<i>Gathering stories.</i>

59:35.506 --> 59:38.817
<i>A story, it belongs to you.</i>

59:39.243 --> 59:41.746
<i>They say that it's gone now.</i>

59:42.980 --> 59:46.257
<i>You know that I disagree.</i>

